0.title: Working Cash-Stabilization Reserve Fund; authorize additional transfer to alleviate the deficit for FY2016.
0.description: An Act To Amend Section 27-103-203, Mississippi Code Of 1972, To Authorize The Executive Director Of The Department Of Finance And Administration To Transfer Working Cash-stabilization Reserve Funds To The General Fund In An Amount Determined By The Governor To Alleviate The Deficit For Fiscal Year 2016.
